sequenceDiagram
    actor SuperAdmin as Super Admin
    participant UI as JavaFX User and Settings Screens
    participant API as Spring Boot Administration API
    participant Service as UserService / SystemSettingService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Audit as AuditLogDAO

    SuperAdmin->>UI: Onboard, update, change role, or deactivate user
    UI->>API: User management command
    API->>Service: enforce super_admin role
    Service->>DB: Insert or update users
    Service->>Audit: Write user lifecycle audit
    API-->>UI: User operation result

    SuperAdmin->>UI: Update system setting
    UI->>API: PUT /system-settings/{key}
    API->>Service: validate non-blank value
    Service->>DB: Update system_settings
    Service->>Audit: Write SYSTEM_CONFIG_UPDATED
    API-->>UI: Setting update result
